title: Nautilus Pull Glitch
body:
So i played i ranked match using Nautilus just before and whenever his pull (e) hits something flash icons fly out of the his anchor, Is this texture glitch happening for everyone, or just me?
{{champion:111}}

replies.body:
His pull is not his e though.
I will quickly have a custom game to investigate if you mean his q.

Edit: Nothing abnormal in my custom game.
Yes, sorry i meant his (q). Try and hook a wall or something, thats where i noticed it a lot
